df_fan = pd.read_csv('web_scrape_data\web_scrape_fan.csv')

Assigning a type column for each PC part dataframe¶

In [4]:
df_gpu['Type'] = 'Graphics card'
df_cpu['Type'] = 'Processor'
df_mobo['Type'] = 'Motherboard'
df_ram['Type'] = 'Memory'
df_ssd['Type'] = 'Solid State Drive'
df_psu['Type'] = 'Power supply'
df_case['Type'] = 'Case'
df_fan['Type'] = 'CPU/GPU fan'

Merging all the data into a single dataframe¶

In [5]:
df = pd.concat([df_gpu, df_cpu, df_mobo, df_ram, df_ssd, df_psu, df_case, df_fan])

Converting the dataframe into a Styler object to make the Url:s into hyperlink format¶

In [33]:
def url_hyperlink(x):
    return '<a href="{}">{}</a>'.format(x,x)

new_df = df.reset_index(drop=True).style.format({'Url': url_hyperlink})
